gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Jazz 132, Pacers 105
gameRecap.excerpt: The Jazz win their sixth straight game as they defeat the Pacers, 132-105. Lauri Markkanen recorded 32 points (10-15 FG) and 10 rebounds for the Jazz, while Collin Sexton added a season-high 30 points (4-5 3PT FG), along with five assists in the victory. Buddy Hield tallied 14 points (3-5 3PT FG) for the Pacers in the losing effort. The Jazz improve to 22-20 on the season, while the Pacers fall to 23-17.
